Mail-DKIM version 0.19
======================

This module implements the various components of the DKIM message-signing
and verifying standard for Internet mail. It currently implements
Internet Draft draft-ietf-dkim-base-01.

INSTALLATION

To install this module type the following:

   perl Makefile.PL
   make
   make test
   make install

DEPENDENCIES

This module requires these other modules and libraries:

  Crypt::OpenSSL::RSA
  Digest::SHA
  Digest::SHA1
  Error
  Mail::Address (part of the MailTools package)
  MIME::Base64
  Net::DNS

USAGE

Decide whether you want to "sign" or "verify" messages.
To sign, see the Mail::DKIM::Signer module.
To verify, see the Mail::DKIM::Verifier module.

BUGS

The current draft as of this writing, draft-ietf-dkim-base-02.txt of
May 2006, is not yet supported.

Report bugs to Jason Long <jlong@messiah.edu>.

